  <constraints>
    <constraint source="architecture-§5">DO NOT use `spaarke-insights-index`, `MultiIndexComposer`, `InsightsOrchestrator`, `EvidenceSufficiencyNode`, `GroundingVerifyNode`, `sprk_matter.sprk_performancesummary` for chat memory. Verify zero references from chat-routing/memory code.</constraint>
