  <steps>
    <step order="1">Locate the Insights regression test suite under `tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/Services/Ai/Insights/` (or equivalent path).</step>
    <step order="2">Run the suite: `dotnet test --filter "Category=Insights"` (or equivalent filter).</step>
    <step order="3">Grep verification: confirm zero chat-routing or memory code references the 6 binding-NEGATIVE assets:
      - `grep -rn "spaarke-insights-index" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/` → 0 hits
      - `grep -rn "MultiIndexComposer" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Memory/` → 0 hits (Insights/ dir OK)
      - `grep -rn "InsightsOrchestrator" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/" → 0 hits
      - `grep -rn "EvidenceSufficiencyNode" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/` → 0 hits
      - `grep -rn "GroundingVerifyNode" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/` → 0 hits
      - `grep -rn "sprk_performancesummary" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/" → 0 hits</step>
    <step order="4">Verify `sprk_matter.sprk_performancesummary` field has zero chat-side reads/writes via Dataverse audit query if available.</step>
    <step order="5">Author report at `notes/handoffs/145-insights-regression.md` documenting: suite results, grep verification table, Dataverse check outcome, compliance with NFR-06 + success criterion #15.</step>
    <step order="6">If any binding-NEGATIVE component referenced from chat-routing code, escalate per CLAUDE.md §6.</step>
    <step order="7">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 145 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

